 1990-19041990-08-280,  OLD INAC,  ,  , 
PrecisOrder which provides for: (a) the acceptance of the transfer from the Province of NOVA SCOTIA of the administration and control over some 43.4 hectares of land situate in the County of ANTIGONISH; and (b) the setting apart of those lands for the use and benefit of the AFTON BAND of Indians as Summerside Indian Reserve No. 38.
